description: This data set contains the current data for the Molecular Analysis for Therapy Choice (MATCH Z1D) precision medcine clincal trial program extracted from the NCI GDC. See https://www.cancer.gov/about-cancer/treatment/clinical-trials/nci-supported/nci-match for more information. The tables within this data set are dynamic and update with new releases; for static tables use MATCH_versioned.
